      "comment": "BROTHER ERNEST (4) lines up chasing another win after rocketing around the Angle Park 530m in 30.19 on February 23. Hot win latest and looks the one to beat again. DAKOTA RYLEN (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when eighth at Angle Park over 342m behind You Ain't It (20.38) in a Best 8. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can do much better this time. PAW EVA (6) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (22.61) last time in a Grade 5 at Murray Bridge. Can do much better this time. MEMORIES OF ROSE (8) was a huge winner last start. Hard to beat again.",
